{"title":"linux查看用户组和用户信息","date":"2023-07-28T17:40:19.003Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2023年7月28日","L":"2023/07/28","MM-DD":"07-28"},"link":"2023/07/28/linux查看用户组和用户信息","updated":"2023-07-28T08:58:10.390Z","content":"<p>查看所有用户组和用户信息</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">cat /etc/passwd</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>查看当前登陆用户所在的组</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">groups</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>查看特定组包含的用户</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">#举例：查询组名为kali的成员</span><br><span class=\"line\">#先查询kali的组号</span><br><span class=\"line\">grep &#x27;kali&#x27; /etc/group</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">#查看到kali所在组号为1000</span><br><span class=\"line\">#查询组号为1000的所有成员</span><br><span class=\"line\">awk -F&quot;:&quot; &#x27;&#123;print $1&quot;\\t\\t&quot;$4&#125;&#x27; /etc/passwd | grep &#x27;1000&#x27;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/bfab24f84b6b4bc0843c445e98492708.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n","prev":{"title":"kali-linux-2021.2-installer-amd64安装教程","link":"2023/07/28/kali-linux-2021.2-installer-amd64安装教程"},"next":{"title":"Java实现批量生成txt文件，并在文件中插入内容","link":"2023/07/28/Java实现批量生成txt文件，并在文件中插入内容"}